    "created_at": "2015-12-11T08:12:18Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-12-11T08:12:18Z",
    "body": "Our [node message loop integration](https://github.com/atom/electron/blob/master/atom/common/node_bindings_mac.cc#L46) relies on `uv_backend_timeout` to determine how long we should wait before the next event iteration, it seems that in the test case it is returning the wrong `timeout` after a few DNS lookups.\n\nIt could be a bug of libuv, but it also may because we are using `uv_backend_timeout` wrong, we are calling it in a new thread while it is not thread safe.\n"
  },
